Package com.w10.risk_game.models.phases

Class PlaySetupPhase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.w10.risk_game.models.Phase
      • com.w10.risk_game.models.phases.GamePlayPhase
        • com.w10.risk_game.models.phases.PlaySetupPhase
  • public class PlaySetupPhase
extends GamePlayPhase
    The PlaySetupPhase class is a subclass of GamePlayPhase that handles the setup phase of the game, including creating and removing players, assigning countries, and transitioning to the main play phase.
    Author:
    Sherwyn Dsouza
